sentences.sentence: I was majored in Administrative Management during my undergraduate corse.
sentences.translation: 我的专业是行政管理本科课程期间。

sentences.sentence: Frankly speaking, I always consider myself as a vulgar and corse person. I think I have seen through this society.
sentences.translation: 说真的，我一直以为我自己是个特别粗俗的人，我想我把这个社会上的种种都看透了。

sentences.sentence: Now I would like to apply learning in e-government, because it will be more consistent with my major that I studied during undergraduate corse.
sentences.translation: 现在，我想在电子政务运用学习，因为这将是我跟我的专业研究在本科科西嘉更加一致的。
